"{\"uid\": \"eonline.com-news-1406857-what-to-know-about-rebecca-cheptegei-the-olympic-runner-set-on-fire-in-a-gasoline-attack\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Ugandan distance runner Rebecca Cheptegei died due to severe burns after, police say, a man she allegedly dated doused her with gasoline and set her on fire.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 157, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 24, \"end\": 31, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\", \"score\": 0.978419392463279, \"rank\": 0.022056602416962716, \"text\": \"Rebecca\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Aug. 11,Rebecca Cheptegeifinished in the middle of the pack of thewomen's marathonat the2024 Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 159, \"to\": 270, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 255, \"end\": 269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Weeks later, she was fighting for her life at a hospital in Kenya.\", \"from\": 272, \"to\": 338, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 332, \"end\": 337, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.030548585861967e-27, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 33-year-old distance runner suffered burns over more than 75 percent of her body after a man, referred to by authorities as her boyfriend,doused her with gasoline and set her on fireat her home in Trans-Nzoia County on Sept. 1, according to local police.\", \"from\": 340, \"to\": 598, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 541, \"end\": 559, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trans-Nzoia_County\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Trans-Nzoia County\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trans-Nzoia_County\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trans-Nzoia_County\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Theathlete died Sept. 5,local outlets confirmed.\", \"from\": 599, \"to\": 647, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dickson Ndiema Marangach, the alleged perpetrator, also suffered \\\"serious burns\\\" and they were both being treated at Moi Teaching and Referral Hospital in the city of Eldoret, Trans-Nzoia County Police CommanderJeremiah ole Kosiomtold Kenyan paperThe Star.\", \"from\": 649, \"to\": 905, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 649, \"end\": 656, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_Dickson\", \"score\": 0.9995863664450205, \"rank\": 0.0004132819468456332, \"text\": \"Dickson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_Dickson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_Dickson\"}, {\"begin\": 825, \"end\": 843, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trans-Nzoia_County\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Trans-Nzoia County\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trans-Nzoia_County\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trans-Nzoia_County\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the time, Cheptegei-a Ugandan-born athlete living in Kenya to be closer to elite training facilities-was in critical condition with external and inhalation burns, MTRH CEO Dr.OwenMenachtold reportersoutside the hospital.\", \"from\": 907, \"to\": 1130, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 963, \"end\": 968, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.030548585861967e-27, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She is a high-profile patient,\\\" he added, \\\"and we are doing all we can to save her life.\\\"\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1222, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"According to Kosiom, neighbors heard Cheptegei and Ndiema arguing on Sept. 1 at her home in Endebess, Kenya.\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1332, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1316, \"end\": 1324, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Endebess\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Endebess\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Endebess\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Endebess\"}, {\"begin\": 1326, \"end\": 1331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.030548585861967e-27, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then, the commander said, Ndiema left, purchased a 5-liter can of gasoline and returned to Cheptegei's residence.\", \"from\": 1333, \"to\": 1446, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The couple were heard quarrelling outside their house,\\\" Kosiom toldKenya'sThe Standard.\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1536, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"During the altercation, the boyfriend was seen pouring a liquid on the woman before burning her.\\\"\", \"from\": 1537, \"to\": 1635, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The disturbing attack comes amid rising outrage over the scourge of violence against women in Kenya, where, according to the Africa Data Hub (which tracks media reports on such incidents), at least 500 women and girls have been murdered since 2016.\", \"from\": 1637, \"to\": 1885, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1731, \"end\": 1736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.030548585861967e-27, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\"}, {\"begin\": 1762, \"end\": 1768, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999999677129, \"rank\": 2.4861192086930845e-11, \"text\": \"Africa\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The shocking reality that at least 10 women have been killed in the first month of 2024 alone intensifies an already troubling trend,\\\"Mary Njeri, a gender-based violence analyst,told UN Womenin February.\", \"from\": 1887, \"to\": 2091, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2071, \"end\": 2073, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\", \"score\": 0.9112487090468675, \"rank\": 0.09728072651449515, \"text\": \"UN\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Nations\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Each loss is a stark indicator of the systemic issues we are striving to dismantle.\\\"\", \"from\": 2092, \"to\": 2177, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As the community mourns yet another death, here is more to know about Cheptegei:  Cheptegui was born Feb. 22, 1991, and grew up in Cheminy, in the east African nation of Uganda.\", \"from\": 2179, \"to\": 2356, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2349, \"end\": 2355, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.227586269098993e-28, \"text\": \"Uganda\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her dadJoseph Cheptegeitold reporters that his daughter is a married mother of two daughters, age 9 and 11, and their father lives in Uganda.\", \"from\": 2358, \"to\": 2499, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2492, \"end\": 2498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.227586269098993e-28, \"text\": \"Uganda\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She's been competing professionally in distance races since 2010, according to World Athletics, with herfirst listed resultbeing a 4-minute, 20.49-second 15th-place finish in the 1,500-meters at the 38th IAAF World Cross Country Championships that year in Poland.\", \"from\": 2501, \"to\": 2764, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2580, \"end\": 2595, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"score\": 0.9999999993965503, \"rank\": 6.033635590194381e-10, \"text\": \"World Athletics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\"}, {\"begin\": 2705, \"end\": 2709, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"IAAF\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\"}, {\"begin\": 2710, \"end\": 2743, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_Cross_Country_Championships\", \"score\": 0.9999933844711089, \"rank\": 6.615561064860992e-06, \"text\": \"World Cross Country Championships\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_Cross_Country_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_Cross_Country_Championships\"}, {\"begin\": 2757, \"end\": 2763, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland\", \"score\": 0.9891979390180787, \"rank\": 0.007824165780746729, \"text\": \"Poland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2022, she won the Padova Marathon in Italy and finished second in the 10,000-meters at the Ugandan Championships, as well as triumphed in the women's up-and-down mountain race at the the inaugural World Mountain and Trail Running Championships in Chiang Mai, Thailand.\", \"from\": 2766, \"to\": 3037, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2806, \"end\": 2811, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.9646410540536176, \"rank\": 0.036654125277643404, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}, {\"begin\": 3016, \"end\": 3026, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chiang_Mai\", \"score\": 0.9999908616218003, \"rank\": 5.428453009652601e-06, \"text\": \"Chiang Mai\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chiang_Mai\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chiang_Mai\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She capped off that year finishing in fourth place in the 2022 ADNOC Abu Dhabi Marathon with a personal best time of 2:22:47.\", \"from\": 3039, \"to\": 3164, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Cheptegei finished 14th in the marathon at the2023 World Athletic Championshipsin Budapest last summer and was one of 25 athletes who qualified to represent Uganda at the 2024 Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 3166, \"to\": 3357, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3248, \"end\": 3256, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.7442299970690034e-12, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}, {\"begin\": 3323, \"end\": 3329, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.227586269098993e-28, \"text\": \"Uganda\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the Summer Games, where she made her Olympics debut, she finished 44th (of 91 runners, 11 of whom did not finish) in the women's marathon with a time of 2:32:14.\", \"from\": 3359, \"to\": 3523, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ugandan Olympic Committee presidentDonald Rukareslammed the attack on Cheptegei as \\\"totally unacceptable.\\\"\", \"from\": 3525, \"to\": 3631, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3525, \"end\": 3532, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.829776621703678e-20, \"text\": \"Ugandan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Let us keep Rebecca in pray [sic] and wish her a full recovery,\\\" heposted on X Sept. 3.\", \"from\": 3633, \"to\": 3721, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3646, \"end\": 3653, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\", \"score\": 0.978419392463279, \"rank\": 0.022056602416962716, \"text\": \"Rebecca\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Let us all say NO to violence especially against women.\", \"from\": 3722, \"to\": 3778, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is totally unacceptable and we condemn this totally uncalled for attack.\", \"from\": 3779, \"to\": 3856, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Together let us stand against violence.\\\"\", \"from\": 3857, \"to\": 3897, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hecontinued, \\\"This is heartbreaking and completely unacceptable.\", \"from\": 3899, \"to\": 3963, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No one should ever have to endure such violence, especially someone as inspiring as Rebecca.\", \"from\": 3964, \"to\": 4056, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4048, \"end\": 4055, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\", \"score\": 0.978419392463279, \"rank\": 0.022056602416962716, \"text\": \"Rebecca\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We must all stand together and say NO to violence against women.\", \"from\": 4057, \"to\": 4121, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us keep Rebecca in our thoughts and prayers, and work towards a society where such acts are condemned and eradicated.\", \"from\": 4122, \"to\": 4243, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4134, \"end\": 4141, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\", \"score\": 0.978419392463279, \"rank\": 0.022056602416962716, \"text\": \"Rebecca\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wishing her a full and speedy recovery.\", \"from\": 4244, \"to\": 4283, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"#NoToViolence #StandWithRebecca.\\\"\", \"from\": 4284, \"to\": 4317, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While police referred to Marangach as Cheptegei's boyfriend, her father told reporters outside the hospital, perThe Star, \\\"They were just friends, and I wonder why he wanted to take things away belonging to my daughter.\\\"\", \"from\": 4319, \"to\": 4539, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Standing alongside Cheptegei's sisterEvalyne Chelagat, the family patriarch pleaded for justice.\", \"from\": 4541, \"to\": 4637, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Marangach suffered burns over 30 percent of his body in the fire and was in better condition than Cheptegei, according to hospital CEO Menach.\", \"from\": 4639, \"to\": 4781, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4774, \"end\": 4780, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Menach\", \"score\": 0.9999999999931788, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Menach\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Menach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Menach\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Police commander KosiomtoldThe Standardthat Marangach snuck into Cheptegei's home at around 2 p.m. on Sept. 1 while she and her children were at church.\", \"from\": 4783, \"to\": 4935, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Upon returning, Dickson, who had procured petrol, began pouring it on Rebecca before he set her ablaze,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 4936, \"to\": 5050, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4953, \"end\": 4960, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_Dickson\", \"score\": 0.9995863664450205, \"rank\": 0.0004132819468456332, \"text\": \"Dickson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_Dickson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brian_Dickson\"}, {\"begin\": 5007, \"end\": 5014, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\", \"score\": 0.978419392463279, \"rank\": 0.022056602416962716, \"text\": \"Rebecca\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Eventually, he continued, \\\"The two were rescued by neighbors who put out the fire and rushed them to hospital.\\\"\", \"from\": 5051, \"to\": 5162, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Investigators found an empty gas can and a fire-damaged mobile phone they believe belonged to Cheptegei, Kosiom said.\", \"from\": 5164, \"to\": 5281, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The commander also said Cheptegei and Marangach had been involved in a protracted dispute over land that was headed to court and were known to have argued about it before.\", \"from\": 5283, \"to\": 5454, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And amid reports that called the attack a domestic dispute, Cheptegei's dad Josephre-emphasizedthat his daughter was not romantically involved with Marangach.\", \"from\": 5456, \"to\": 5614, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I wish to state that my wounded daughter is married and her husband is in Uganda,\\\" he toldThe Standard.\", \"from\": 5616, \"to\": 5720, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5691, \"end\": 5697, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.227586269098993e-28, \"text\": \"Uganda\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Her attacker was a friend they met in Kenya and my daughter trusted him.\", \"from\": 5721, \"to\": 5794, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5760, \"end\": 5765, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.030548585861967e-27, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They fell out recently but the suspect sneaked into her compound on Sunday afternoon, armed with five litres of petrol and hid in a poultry house.\\\"\", \"from\": 5795, \"to\": 5942, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Cheptegei was first rushed to Kitale County Referral Hospital before being transferred to Moi Teaching and Referral Hospital for specialized treatment, according to authorities.\", \"from\": 5944, \"to\": 6121, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5974, \"end\": 5980, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kitale\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kitale\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kitale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kitale\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hospitalized at MTRH, \\\"in critical condition and under support,\\\" anaesthesiologist and Critical Care specialist Dr.Josephat KerematoldThe StandardSept.\", \"from\": 6123, \"to\": 6274, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"3, \\\"we are in the initial stage of management as we assess Rebecca.\\\"\", \"from\": 6275, \"to\": 6343, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6334, \"end\": 6341, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\", \"score\": 0.978419392463279, \"rank\": 0.022056602416962716, \"text\": \"Rebecca\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebecca\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said that, in addition to the skin damage, the inhalation burns she sustained affected her throat and airwaves, and doctors were working to prevent multi-organ failure.\", \"from\": 6345, \"to\": 6516, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Cheptegei's father told the publication that her children were being cared for by their grandmother.\", \"from\": 6518, \"to\": 6618, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Her children are crying in the house after hearing about the attack,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 6620, \"to\": 6699, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have asked my wife to take care of them as we hope for my daughter's recovery.\\\"\", \"from\": 6700, \"to\": 6782, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your source for entertainment news, celebrities, celeb news, and \\u200bcelebrity gossip.\", \"from\": 6784, \"to\": 6867, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Check out the hottest fashion, photos, movies and TV shows!\", \"from\": 6868, \"to\": 6927, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a92025E!\", \"from\": 6929, \"to\": 6936, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Entertainment Television, LLC A Versant Media Company.\", \"from\": 6937, \"to\": 6991, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6963, \"end\": 6966, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_liability_company\", \"score\": 0.999999435946097, \"rank\": 5.640540797645751e-07, \"text\": \"LLC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_liability_company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_liability_company\"}, {\"begin\": 6969, \"end\": 6976, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Versant\", \"score\": 0.999999986965122, \"rank\": 1.0975827889468282e-08, \"text\": \"Versant\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Versant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Versant\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 6992, \"to\": 7012, \"entities\": []}]}"